---
import ThemeToggle from './ThemeToggle.astro';
---

<div class="container">
  <ThemeToggle />
  <h1>
    <img src="/favicon.png" />
    &nbsp;Moby Slack Application
  </h1>
  <p>Welcome to Triple Whale's support page for the Moby Slack application!</p>
  <p>
    If you already have an{' '}
    <a href="https://app.triplewhale.com/api-keys" target="_blank">API Key</a>,
    you can install the application using the button below. Keep going to read
    more about the application, how to generate a key, and more.
  </p>
  <p>
    {
      /* <a href="https://slack.com/oauth/v2/authorize?client_id=1104768084804.6206138226722&scope=app_mentions:read,channels:history,chat:write,commands,groups:history,im:history,im:write,reactions:write,mpim:history&user_scope="> */
    }
    <a href="https://app.triplewhale.com/api/v2/willy-slackbot/slack/install">
      <img
        alt="Add to Slack"
        height="40"
        width="139"
        src="https://platform.slack-edge.com/img/add_to_slack.png"
        srcset="https://platform.slack-edge.com/img/add_to_slack.png 1x, https://platform.slack-edge.com/img/add_to_slack@2x.png 2x"
      />
    </a>
  </p>

  <h2 id="about-moby">
    <a href="#about-moby" class="header-link"> 🐳 About Moby </a>
  </h2>
  <div class="videoWrapper">
    <iframe
      width="560"
      height="315"
      src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/BqjtGpBqz8I?si=4JSJi2u3GG-cUGWR"
      title="YouTube video player"
      frameborder="0"
      allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
      referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin"
      allowfullscreen
    >
    </iframe>
  </div>
  <p>
    Moby is your trusty assistant for all things e-commerce & marketing on
    Triple Whale! Whether you're a marketing pro or an e-commerce manager,
    Moby's got your back. From crunching numbers and forecasting trends to
    optimizing your ad spend & uncovering insights, Moby makes data-driven
    decisions a breeze. Just ask, and Moby will dive deep into your data,
    surfacing actionable insights & innovative strategies to boost your
    business. 🌊📈
  </p>

  <h2 id="about-slack-app">
    <a href="#about-slack-app" class="header-link"> 💬 About The Slack App </a>
  </h2>
  <p>
    The Slack application allows a team to add Moby directly into their slack
    workspace, and specify per-user the store they wish to chat with Moby about.
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>Note:</strong> To use Moby, you need to be on the Enterprise plan, and
    have an API key.
  </p>

  <h2 id="getting-api-key">
    <a href="#getting-api-key" class="header-link"> 🔑 Getting Your API Key </a>
  </h2>
  <p>
    In the Triple Whale application, navigate to{' '}
    <a href="https://app.triplewhale.com/api-keys" target="_blank"
      >Settings > API Keys</a
    >, and click "Generate" to create a new API key.
    <p>
      <strong>Note:</strong> Make sure to check <i>ALL</i> the boxes.
    </p>
  </p>

  <h2 id="setting-up">
    <a href="#setting-up" class="header-link"> 🔄 Setting Up Moby in Slack </a>
  </h2>
  <p>
    After downloading the Moby Slack App, search for Moby in slack. Select the
    Moby app.
  </p>

  <p>
    Enter your <code>myshopify.com</code> URL, your <code>API Key</code>, and
    test the connection.
  </p>

  <h3>Connection Results</h3>
  <p>
    Check the messages section to see the connect result. Potential results:
  </p>

  <div class="box">
    <p>
      ✅ <strong
        >Your configuration is valid, and you are connected to your shop! 🎉</strong
      ><br />
      Means that the connection was successful and you can start using Moby in Slack.
    </p>

    <p>
      ⚠️ <strong
        >Your configuration is invalid! Please update your values and try again!
        😢</strong
      ><br />
      Means that the connection did not work. Ensure that:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Your myshopify url is correct</li>
      <li>Your api key is correct</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      ⚠️ <strong
        >Please provide your Shop ID and API key, and try again! 😢</strong
      ><br />
      Means that you did not include the Shopify URL and/or the API Key in the connection
      test. Ensure that:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Your myshopify url is filled out</li>
      <li>Your api key is filled out</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <h2 id="interacting">
    <a href="#interacting" class="header-link">
      💬 Interacting with Moby in Slack
    </a>
  </h2>

  <ul>
    <li>
      When you send a message, Moby reacts with a thinking face 🤔 meaning he is
      processing and creating a response.
    </li>

    <li>
      Once the response is sent, Moby reacts with a check mark ✅ and will reply
      in a thread to your message.
    </li>

    <li>Open the thread to view the response and continue the conversation.</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    <strong>Important:</strong> Moby will be able to reply to you even if you are
    not connected to your account. However, it will not use any relevant data. If
    this happens, test your connection with steps previously outlined.
  </p>

  <h2 id="ways-to-chat">
    <a href="#ways-to-chat" class="header-link"> 📱 Ways to Chat with Moby </a>
  </h2>
  <h3>Direct Messages</h3>
  <p>
    In the Moby Slack App, you can message Moby directly in private messages.
  </p>

  <h3>Channel Communication</h3>
  <p>
    In the Moby Slack App, you can add Moby to any channel, public or private.
    Simply send <code>@Moby</code> as a message. You will be prompted to add Moby
    to the channel. Once in the channel, you can send messages with <code
      >@Moby</code
    > command and he will respond.
  </p>

  <h2 id="features">
    <a href="#features" class="header-link"> 📙 Features </a>
  </h2>
  <p>
    You can chat with Moby about various topics, including but not limited to:
  </p>
  <div class="box">
    <p>
      📊 &nbsp; Fetching your Triple Whale metrics, such as ROAS or Net Profit
    </p>
    <p>🛠️ &nbsp; How to set up, work with, and debug Triple Whale features</p>
    <p>🎯 &nbsp; Questions about your store, ads, or creatives</p>
    <p>🛍️ &nbsp; General questions about e-commerce</p>
    <p>📅 &nbsp; Create and schedule reports</p>
    <p>✨ &nbsp; Much more!</p>
  </div>

  <h2 id="installation">
    <a href="#installation" class="header-link"> 🏁 Installation </a>
  </h2>
  <p>To install the Slack app, simply click the "Add to Slack" button below:</p>
  <p>
    {
      /* <a href="https://slack.com/oauth/v2/authorize?client_id=1104768084804.6206138226722&scope=app_mentions:read,channels:history,chat:write,commands,groups:history,im:history,im:write,reactions:write,mpim:history&user_scope="> */
    }
    <a href="https://app.triplewhale.com/api/v2/willy-slackbot/slack/install">
      <img
        alt="Add to Slack"
        height="40"
        width="139"
        src="https://platform.slack-edge.com/img/add_to_slack.png"
        srcset="https://platform.slack-edge.com/img/add_to_slack.png 1x, https://platform.slack-edge.com/img/add_to_slack@2x.png 2x"
      />
    </a>
  </p>

  <h2 id="support">
    <a href="#support" class="header-link"> 💁 Support </a>
  </h2>
  <p>
    We have a comprehensive{' '}
    <a
      href="https://kb.triplewhale.com/en/collections/8945112-chat-with-data"
      target="_blank">Knowledge Base</a
    >
    {' '}
    on chatting with data, which includes videos, guides, and tips for how to best
    utilize Moby's features.
  </p>
  <p>
    If you need any assistance or have questions, you can
    <a href="https://kb.triplewhale.com/" target="_blank"
      >reach our support team directly</a
    >; simply click the chat bubble in the bottom right corner of the page.
  </p>

  <footer>
    <p>
      <a target="_blank" href="https://triplewhale.com">Triple Whale</a>
    </p>
    <p>
      <a target="_blank" href="https://www.triplewhale.com/pages/privacy-notice"
        >Privacy Policy</a
      >
      <a
        target="_blank"
        href="https://www.triplewhale.com/pages/terms-of-service"
        >Terms and Conditions</a
      >
      <a target="_blank" href="https://kb.triplewhale.com/en/">Privacy Policy</a
      >
    </p>
  </footer>
</div>
